divs: Sighting DetailsSighting Report: On February 24 at l1:31 I was up walking the house, I looked out my back window, I was a bright Light-traveling South, It was probably the size of a large truck. Traveling pretty fast. I watched it and in about 2 minutes it was out of sight. No Noise . I know you think I am crazy mut I always know when they are around me. Thanks.
